            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-de4661-Hd1e108">Rubrica 18</head>
            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-de4661-Hd1e111" type="question-title">De iuramenti religione</head>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de4661-d1e114">
               <lb ed="#V" n="59"/>¶ De iuramenti religione. Rubrica. 18
    </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de4661-d1e119">
               <lb ed="#V" n="60"/> <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-de4661-Rd1e116">IN leuitico. cap. 19.</ref>
      <lb ed="#V" n="61"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de4661-Qd1e125" source="http://scta.info/resource/lev19_12@1-10">Non 
               per<lb ed="#V" n="62" break="no"/>iurabis in nomine meo: nec 
               pollu<lb ed="#V" n="63" break="no"/>es nomen domini dei tui.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de4661-d1e133">
               <lb ed="#V" n="64"/>
             <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-de4661-Rd1e132">¶ Iesus filius sirach in ecclesiastico. cap. 23.</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="65"/> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de4661-Qd1e137" source="http://scta.info/resource/sir23_9@1-10 http://scta.info/resource/sir23_12@1-5">Iurationi non assuescat os tuum: multi enim
        <lb ed="#V" n="66"/>casus in illa. Uir multum iurans implebitur
        <lb ed="#V" n="67"/>iniquitate.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de4661-d1e148">
               <lb ed="#V" n="68"/>
             <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-de4661-Rd1e149">¶ Mattheus in euange. c. 5.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de4661-Qd1e152" source="http://scta.info/resource/mt5_34@5-14  http://scta.info/resource/mt5_35@1-16  http://scta.info/resource/mt5_36@1-14  http://scta.info/resource/mt5_37@1-16">Non iurare 
               omni<lb ed="#V" n="69" break="no"/>no: neque per caelum quia thronus dei est: neque per
        <lb ed="#V" n="70"/>terram: quia scabellum est pedum eius: neque per 
               hiero<lb ed="#V" n="71" break="no"/>solymam quia ciuitas est magni regis: nec per
        <lb ed="#V" n="72"/>caput tuum iurabis: quia non potes vnum capillum
        <lb ed="#V" n="73"/>album facere aut nigrum. Sit autem sermo vester
        <lb ed="#V" n="74"/>est est non non: quod autem his habundantius est
        <lb ed="#V" n="75"/>a malo est.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de4661-d1e171">
               <lb ed="#V" n="76"/>
             <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-de4661-Rd1e174">¶ Iacobus apostolus epistola vnica. c. 5. et fi.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de4661-Qd1e175" source="http://scta.info/resource/iac5_12@6-24">
               No<lb ed="#V" n="77" break="no"/>lite iurare neque per caelum neque per terram: neque
        <lb ed="#V" n="78"/>aliud quodcumque iuramentum: sit sermo vester
        <lb ed="#V" n="79"/>est est non non.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de4661-d1e185">
               <lb ed="#V" n="80"/>
             <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-de4661-Rd1e190">/ Paulus apostolus epstola ad hebreos. c. 6.</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="81"/> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de4661-Qd1e189" source="http://scta.info/resource/hebr6_16@1-15">Homines per maiorem sui iurant: et omnis
        <lb ed="#V" n="82"/>controuersie eorum finis. Ad 
               confirmatio<lb ed="#V" n="83" break="no"/>nem est iuramentum.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de4661-d1e199">
               <lb ed="#V" n="84"/>
                <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-de4661-Rd1e206">¶ Cato. c. i. iusiurandum serua.</ref> <!--I believe this is just a reference-->
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de4661-d1e207">
               <lb ed="#V" n="85"/>
                <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-de4661-Rd1e215">¶ Isidorus solilo. lib. 2. c. 35.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de4661-Qd1e211">Assiduitas 
               iu<lb ed="#V" n="86" break="no"/>randi periurii consuetudinem facit. Usus
        <lb ed="#V" n="87"/>iurandi ad periurium ducit. Sit in ore tuo
        <lb ed="#V" n="88"/>est: sit in ore tuo non est: veritas 
               iuramen<lb ed="#V" n="89" break="no"/>to non indiget.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de4661-d1e223"> 
      <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de4661-Qd1e225">/ Firma sit sacramenti tui
        <lb ed="#V" n="90"/>fides. <!--35.xml-->
        <pb ed="#V" n="6-v"/>
                  <cb ed="#V" n="a"/>
               </quote>
            </p>
         </div>
